{"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["# Stanford RNA 3D Folding Part 2 — Colab 一键运行\n","\n","本 Notebook 在 Google Colab 上：\n","1. 安装依赖\n","2. 配置 Kaggle API 并自动下载比赛数据（可仅下载 CSV 轻量模式）\n","3. 运行训练\n","\n","**使用前**：在 Kaggle 网站 Account -> Create New API Token 下载 `kaggle.json`，在下面「上传 kaggle.json」单元格中上传。"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 1. 检测 Colab 并安装依赖"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["# 检测是否在 Colab\n","try:\n","    import google.colab\n","    IN_COLAB = True\n","    print(\"Running on Google Colab\")\n","except ImportError:\n","    IN_COLAB = False\n","    print(\"Running locally\")"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["# 安装依赖（Colab 已有 torch）\n","!pip install -q kaggle pyyaml pandas numpy scipy\n","print(\"Done.\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 2. 上传 kaggle.json 并配置 API"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["### 可选：挂载 Google Drive\n","\n","若将 `kaggle.json` 或比赛数据放在 Google Drive 中，请先运行下面单元格挂载 Drive。"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["# 挂载后可从 /content/drive/MyDrive/ 读取 kaggle.json 或数据\n","from google.colab import drive\n","drive.mount(\"/content/drive\")\n","print(\"Drive 已挂载: /content/drive/MyDrive\")\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["import os\n","from pathlib import Path\n","\n","os.makedirs(\"/root/.kaggle\", exist_ok=True)\n","\n","# 优先 /content/，其次 Google Drive（需先挂载 Drive）\n","kaggle_src = None\n","if Path(\"/content/kaggle.json\").exists():\n","    kaggle_src = \"/content/kaggle.json\"\n","elif Path(\"/content/drive/MyDrive/kaggle.json\").exists():\n","    kaggle_src = \"/content/drive/MyDrive/kaggle.json\"\n","if kaggle_src:\n","    !cp {kaggle_src} /root/.kaggle/kaggle.json\n","    !chmod 600 /root/.kaggle/kaggle.json\n","    print(\"Kaggle API 已配置:\", kaggle_src)\n","else:\n","    print(\"请上传 kaggle.json 到 /content/ 或放到 Google Drive 的 MyDrive/kaggle.json 后挂载 Drive\")\n","    print(\"获取方式: Kaggle 网站 -> Account -> Create New API Token")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 3. 上传/解压代码库并设置路径"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["# 方式1: 已上传 3drna_cs.zip 到 /content/ 则解压\n","# 方式2: 从 GitHub 克隆（把下面 YOUR_USER/YOUR_REPO 换成你的仓库）\n","# 方式3: 从 Colab 左侧把整个 3drna_cs 文件夹拖进 /content/\n","from pathlib import Path\n","import sys\n","import os\n","\n","if Path(\"/content/3drna_cs.zip\").exists():\n","    !cd /content && unzip -o 3drna_cs.zip && echo \"Unzipped\"\n","\n","REPO_URL = \"https://github.com/scyoyo/3drna_cs\"\n","\n","ROOT = Path(\"/content/3drna_cs\")\n","if not (ROOT.exists() and (ROOT / \"src\").exists()):\n","    !git clone https://github.com/scyoyo/3drna_cs /content/3drna_cs\n","    ROOT = Path(\"/content/3drna_cs\")\n","else:\n","    # 已克隆过则拉取最新代码\n","    !cd /content/3drna_cs && git pull\n","if not (ROOT / \"src\").exists():\n","    cwd = Path(\".\").resolve()\n","    if (cwd / \"src\").exists():\n","        ROOT = cwd\n","    elif (cwd.parent / \"src\").exists():\n","        ROOT = cwd.parent\n","    else:\n","        ROOT = cwd\n","\n","if not (ROOT / \"src\").exists():\n","    raise FileNotFoundError(\"克隆失败。可手动: !git clone https://github.com/scyoyo/3drna_cs /content/3drna_cs\")\n","\n","sys.path.insert(0, str(ROOT))\n","os.chdir(ROOT)\n","print(\"ROOT:\", ROOT)\n","print(\"src exists:\", (ROOT / \"src\").exists())""]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 4. 下载比赛数据"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["# 数据可放在 /content（临时）或 Google Drive（持久）；若 Drive 已有数据可改为下面路径\n","# DATA_DIR = \"/content/drive/MyDrive/stanford-rna-3d-folding-2\"  # 需先挂载 Drive\n","DATA_DIR = \"/content/stanford-rna-3d-folding-2\"\n","\n","from pathlib import Path\n","data_path = Path(DATA_DIR)\n","has_data = (data_path / \"train_sequences.csv\").exists() and (data_path / \"train_labels.csv\").exists()\n","if has_data:\n","    print(\"数据已存在，跳过下载:\", DATA_DIR)\n","else:\n","    data_path.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n","    get_ipython().system(f'python scripts/download_kaggle_data.py --data_dir \"{DATA_DIR}\" --light')\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["# 检查数据\n","from pathlib import Path\n","p = Path(DATA_DIR)\n","for f in [\"train_sequences.csv\", \"train_labels.csv\"]:\n","    print(f\"{f}: exists={ (p / f).exists() }\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## 5. 运行训练"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["# 使用轻量数据训练（无 MSA 时模型仍可跑，MSA 特征会为零）\n","# 若已下载完整数据含 MSA，可去掉 --light 后重新下载，并确保 DATA_DIR 下有 MSA/ 文件夹\n","\n","!python src/train.py --config configs/model.yaml --train_config configs/train.yaml --stage 3d --device cuda --data_dir \"$DATA_DIR\""]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{},"source":["# 可选：挂载 Google Drive 保存 checkpoint\n","from google.colab import drive\n","drive.mount(\"/content/drive\")\n","!mkdir -p /content/drive/MyDrive/3drna_cs_checkpoints\n","!cp -r checkpoints/* /content/drive/MyDrive/3drna_cs_checkpoints/ 2>/dev/null || true\n","print(\"Checkpoints 已复制到 Google Drive\")"]}],"metadata":{"kernelspec":{"display_name":"Python 3","language":"python","name":"python3"},"language_info":{"name":"python","version":"3.10.0"}},"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":4}
